{"tid":625044,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"直播遭癡漢淫吻　美女記者都怒了","createTime":"2018-04-11T06:18:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T07:03:35.000Z","uid":106204,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b6f3f8faf57d3d9f63c5ccf4e5589fc2510add5b","tid":625044,"uid":106204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T06:18:22.000Z","msg":"巴西一名31歲體育女記者迪爾特里(Bruna Dealtry)，日前在進行一場球賽後的訪問直播時，竟突然遭到一名癡漢淫吻，迪爾特里當場大叫一聲「啊」。雖然迪爾特里故作鎮定完成訪問，但事後她發文抗議，更引來其他女記者們的響應，大家對這種癡漢行為，都感到憤怒。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《每日郵報》報導，迪爾特里在這起事件後發文抗議，她說：「我喜歡跟球迷一起慶祝，就算向我淋啤酒、在我身邊跳舞或踩到我的腳也不介意，但今天，我親身體驗到不少女性在球場、地鐵甚至在街上行走時感受到的無力感，我在工作中，別人在未經我同意下，吻了我的嘴唇。我不知道該如何反應，也不了解為何有些人認為他們有權這樣做。」<br />\n<br />\n迪爾特里更說：「那位無禮的騷擾者，應該為他所做的事感到羞愧。我是一名足球記者，我也是一名女性，我理應得到尊重。」迪爾特里的事件，立刻引發其他女記者的響應，52名記者決定團結起來反抗，她們還共同製作了一段長1分鐘的影像，記錄了記者們在攝像機前受到性騷擾的事件，貼上主題標籤「#deixaelatrabalhar」，在葡萄牙文中意即「讓她做自己的工作」(#LetHerDoHerJob)。<br />\n<br />\n這起事件的嚴重程度，甚至促使巴西體育部和國家婦女政策秘書處發起了反性騷運動，鼓勵女性運動員們說出自己在體育行業中受到的騷擾。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180411/1332208/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180411%2F1332208%2F&d=kQgFSJP9XBHiOkgzvsGqHp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=61d3b4d5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180411%2F1332208%2F&h=790c243e\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180411/1332208/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港女櫂呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e51a2f232d232944ac6dbe7df8e974e24650225","tid":625044,"uid":106204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T06:18:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e35791bfd6b3a4b70774d7c5f68fba7f5b36758","tid":625044,"uid":17776,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T06:46:46.000Z","msg":"#LetHerDoHer<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Job</span></span><br />\n<br />\n明白，記者只係兼職<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bc03227358206b3e5cb06da8d949ea7cbdcf068","tid":625044,"uid":125460,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T06:53:37.000Z","msg":"樣子問題"},{"pid":"6f2de752b04628ae707e23a94ee91f7b2acaf71e","tid":625044,"uid":55924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T06:59:41.000Z","msg":"香港女妓者比洋腸錫已經濕哂啦"},{"pid":"6328b95fd2f53c8e1d2602bd6491224e35c291f5","tid":625044,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T07:03:32.000Z","msg":"施旖婕唔報風化案？"},{"pid":"60b23008a6249578840f2425540d18cadc7baa18","tid":625044,"uid":40272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T07:14:17.000Z","msg":"力架"},{"pid":"5112cc43a0ee1275d9e018bd7b65389a6ca684ea","tid":625044,"uid":106204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60b23008a6249578840f2425540d18cadc7baa18","tid":625044,"uid":40272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T07:14:17.000Z","msg":"力架"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T07:03:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}